Package: SimpLin
Type: Package
Title: Simple Linear Regression Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Dharma", "Hoy",
      email = "dharma.hoy@colostate.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package takes an x and y vector of equal length,
    throws an error if they are different length, and then fits
    a simple linear regression model and outputs the fit parameters,
    confidence intervals, residuals, standard errors, and predicted values 
    as a list.
License: There is no license.
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.1.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
